@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam ParticipantPadding 8
skinparam BoxPadding 5
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
hide footbox

actor 操作人员 as User
participant "前端" as FE
participant "ProductionOrderController" as Ctrl
participant "ProductionOrderFacadeServiceImpl" as Svc
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> FE: 填写订单信息并提交
FE -> FE: 表单验证
FE -> Ctrl: POST /production-order

Ctrl -> Svc: save(saveProductionOrderDTO)
Svc -> Svc: DTO转换为ProductionOrderPO

group 编码唯一性校验
  Svc -> DB: 查询订单号是否存在
  DB --> Svc: 返回数量
end

group 编码重复
  Svc --> Ctrl: 抛出业务异常
  Ctrl --> FE: 错误响应
  FE --> User: 显示错误提示
end

group 编码唯一
  Svc -> Svc: 业务规则校验，设置默认值
  Svc -> DB: INSERT订单
end

group 整车订单BOM展开
  Svc -> DB: 查询车型默认BOM
  DB --> Svc: BOM数据
  Svc -> Svc: 展开BOM，计算物料需求与缺口
  Svc -> DB: 批量INSERT子订单与BOM项
end

Svc --> Ctrl: 操作结果
Ctrl --> FE: 成功响应
FE --> User: 刷新列表并提示成功

@enduml